{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> SAVE EDMOND</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1260960/extras/GIF_INTRO.gif?t=1718488826\" /><br>Edmond is a lost fifty-year-old who missed his life. And on top of that, before ending his life, he forgot to set up an automatic reply on his mailbox. Unacceptable. Fortunately for him, <strong>and for you because otherwise there would be no game</strong>, Kairos will send him back to his past to change his destiny!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> WIN POGNON</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1260960/extras/GIF_TRAVAIL.gif?t=1718488826\" /><br>Cross the street and find a passion job that doesn't pay in visibility in order to gain access to high-end vehicles, a suit, and eventually a castle.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> DEVELOP THE CITY</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1260960/extras/VILLE.gif?t=1718488826\" /><br>Edit the city because it's your PROJEEEET and you're going to make it WIN.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> RELEASE YOUR SKILLS</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1260960/extras/GIF_COMPETENCES.gif?t=1718488826\" /><br>Unleash your #skills to #growth your #efficiency. #personaldevelopment<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> BREAKING DOWN SLICES</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1260960/extras/GIF_GLACON.gif?t=1718488826\" /><br>Because why not.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> MEET YOUR NEIGHBORS</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1260960/extras/GIF_BAR_compress.gif?t=1718488826\" /><br>Meet Jamil the manly country boy with refined facial capillarity, Simon the LifeStyle influencer or Godefroy who will help you assert your social positioning.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> MAKE TIPS</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1260960/extras/GIF_FABRIQUER.gif?t=1718488826\" /><br>Rummage through the garbage, collect 5 stones, 6 screws and 2 boards to make a whole series of furniture in one click (because it's a simulation, but it's mostly a video game first!).<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">REPUSHES THE EXTRATERRENT QUENILS</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1260960/extras/GIF_QUENOUILLE.gif?t=1718488826\" /><br>Because always why not.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> ALTERNATIVE ENDINGS</h2><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1260960/extras/FINS_MULTIPLES.gif?t=1718488826\" /><br>Edmond guide for (non-exhaustive possibilities):<br>- Let him destroy capitalism<br>- Go to Mars and become Edmond Musk<br>- Let him be eaten by a dinosaur<br>- ...<br><br><strong>In short Kairos'Light is : </strong><br>Projeeeets, inhabitants with particular whims, business that works at the moment and the energies of the cosmic Christ that makes cabins grow in the trees.<br>Kairos'Light, because why not.<br>A crazy and free adventure.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"PDG du ghetto","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1260960/2d82ff620ae71e1b10676faa529ed14d44ecbdaf.jpg"},{"name":"M\u00e9trosexuel","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1260960/e432b5536859e2edacc0f5a02d608ac1eb6bd8b1.jpg"},{"name":"Friand d'humour douteux","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1260960/ec6c0cbe2d01bff5d68135deb6d3bd2e99c5e6fb.jpg"},{"name":"Contradictions","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1260960/e5ceab6132daf9926216cedc9d17236ddaa5557d.jpg"},{"name":"La vie est belle","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1260960/223bdec10b85a1fa21084f95197570773f8aac